             was indicted for <rs id="t18180114-61-off315" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18180114-61-off315" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180114-61-off315" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18180114-61-cd316" type="crimeDate">26th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180114-61-off315 t18180114-61-cd316"></join>, four curtains, value 3l.; three handkerchiefs, value 8s.; and two shifts, value 6s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18180114-61-victim488" type="victimName">
                        John William 
                        Burt
                     <interp inst="t18180114-61-victim488" type="surname" value="Burt"></interp>
